title: Farokh Sarmad, Social Media, and Success, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO68
description: Farokh Sarmad, better known as @farokhgoodlife, is a college-age entrepreneur and social media mogul who is killing it on Instagram. In this episode, The MFCEO and crew invite him into the studio to discuss the basics of business and badassery.
